{"tid":1810935,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"警賊難分，百鬼夜行 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-01-04T09:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T09:29:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa0cec415c6db9f3d5768e567486f69bd879c87","tid":1810935,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200104/20837026/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F20837026%2F&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDpX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=92041a03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F20837026%2F&h=6135aba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200104/20837026/</a><br />\n<br />\n警賊難分，百鬼夜行 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200104/large/1578044225_e97b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200104%2Flarge%2F1578044225_e97b.jpg&h=04e35294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市面上黑警「橫行」到酷愛左右「撞人」，看到不少片段，直行直過旁人無奈讓路，這些蟹狀物卻是打橫向市民突襲推撞，說是不准阻路，完全沒必要，只是顯威報復或者自high，惡形惡相隨時濫暴，所以有黑警逞兇時，忽然暈低PK，與元朗黑幫大佬猝然倒地之姿有異曲同工之妙，港人莫不稱快。<br />\n<br />\n若報應陸續有來，實在太慢，反而在「警賊難分」現況下之受害者，欲哭無淚。<br />\n<br />\n前線黑警蒙面兼拒示委任證或警員編號，已是心知肚明之「國策」，令歹人有機可乘。一名63歲男子傍晚時在屯門，遇2名年約30歲，短髮健碩之綠衣及黑衣人，自稱便衣探員查身份證，突然發難，搶走他手上載着21萬元現金的紙袋，拔足逃去。<br />\n<br />\n類似的案件一定不止一樁，冒警、真警、警黑勾結，怎分得清？竟有大律師建議：遇「可疑人士」（或「無可疑人士」）截查，應（一）要求出示證件；（二）馬上致電有關分區警署查詢；（三）要求隨對方返警署才出示身份證或接受搜身。<br />\n<br />\n真離地！警賊難分怎查證？手機早被沒收或扔掉，就算打通亦長期無人接聽。即時已被毒打搶劫，送羊入虎口返警署？儍的嗎？總之，你身上有21萬就是錯。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日的香港，已是魑魅魍魎，百鬼夜行。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"e5c409c5b0d2f2e870ce364940bd47f72b4594f6","tid":1810935,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"日期：2020年1月5日 星期日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">新春上水和你行</span><br />\n時間 ： 1500<br />\n地點:上水一號花園(龍豐對面)-&gt;上水黨鐵站C出口<br />\n活動TG頻道：<a href=\"https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwedontlikegreygoodstrader&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDpX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=ab727ae2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">（已獲不反對通知書）</span><br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">銅鑼灣 x 灣仔稅局 和你Lunch</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月6日 星期一<br />\n時間 ： 1245 <br />\n地點 ：時代廣場集合/灣仔稅務局<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDpX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=641028cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a><br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\nencourage<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}